{"tid":1769243,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】IU今日經由仁川機場出發飛往新加坡！手裡提著的是...鼎泰豐的袋子 XD","createTime":"2019-12-04T17:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T10:02:47.000Z","uid":34643,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61ae8289666e3d1e9b878c373ffff1c992614d3b","tid":1769243,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794785.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794785.jpg&h=247721e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU在上週在台灣展開《LOVE, POEM》亞洲巡迴演唱會，接下來6日、7日也將到新加坡舉行演唱會。今日，IU也經由仁川機場出發前往新加坡啦！<br />\n<br />\n她穿著牛仔褲搭配毛茸茸的外套、帽子，看起來很保暖，而她的手裡還提著鼎泰豐的袋子呢（笑）！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ruten.com.tw/s2/6/b4/b2/21644176917682_887.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ruten.com.tw%2Fs2%2F6%2Fb4%2Fb2%2F21644176917682_887.jpg&h=7d574fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794780.jpg&h=6c972f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794781.jpg&h=a03d2f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794783.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794783.jpg&h=e2182861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794773.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794773.jpg&h=3da1e7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794779.jpg&h=ac61fb78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794777.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794777.jpg&h=b9ebe94a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794782.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794782.jpg&h=2eb228ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這次她也提前2天去了新加坡，想起上次10週年演唱會的《IU TV》中，她與IU Team在那邊玩得非常開心，當是IU也表示：「對這些很喜歡觀光的人，我每次只提前一天帶他們來...也不能觀光。大家都很喜歡，我也覺得很好。」他們開啟觀光模式，不停地在吃喝，期待這次演唱會會有《IU TV》啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794769.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794769.png&h=c687e725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-12-04/122385-794772.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-12-04%2F122385-794772.png&h=8c96ef30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（延伸閱讀：結束演唱會後想要聚餐的IU，卻被IU Team回：「是來聚餐的嗎？聚餐太多次違約了！」）<br />\n<br />\n而寵粉絲的IU，這次會給新加坡的粉絲帶來什麼樣的驚喜，也令人期待呢！"},{"pid":"0d1c322a603870c1c9c1ad70f82eb9f958e993d2","tid":1769243,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T17:35:44.000Z","msg":"去到新加坡但見唔到fans<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.12442-15/e15/75269523_159490115440905_1893588735661465903_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=1&amp;oh=3f52ae85f0af45528c76551fbb35884c&amp;oe=5DEA84E1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.12442-15%2Fe15%2F75269523_159490115440905_1893588735661465903_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D1%26oh%3D3f52ae85f0af45528c76551fbb35884c%26oe%3D5DEA84E1&h=2ba4daf7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"681974977b9d58f3c4862e4c62acb782c6301f6d","tid":1769243,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,